Class LabelProperties.InclusionComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • jmr.expansion.LabelProperties.InclusionComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Enclosing class:
    LabelProperties

    public static class LabelProperties.InclusionComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements jmr.descriptor.Comparator<LabelProperties,java.lang.Double>
    Functional class that implements the comparation based on Inclusion. if in the comparation the labels are included it takes the distance of properties as distance. If labels are not included, it return infinity as distance.
